Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
When I'm on Page 02 of Thoracic MRI
Then 'Anamnesis' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Nicotine abuse' from 'Anamnesis' dropdown menu
Then 'Add anamnesis' button is enabled
And 'Pack years' input field is enabled

When I select 'Stent' from 'Anamnesis' dropdown menu
Then 'Add anamnesis' button is enabled
And 'Aortic valve (TAVI)' checkbox is enabled
And 'Coronary' checkbox is enabled
And 'Thoracic aorta (TEVAR)' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'History of partial lung resection' from 'Anamnesis' dropdown menu
Then 'Add anamnesis' button is enabled
And 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled
